  "text": "Cardiovascular disease as a major health issue worldwide has received much more attention than pregnancy hypertension with much more epidemiological data. We have illustrated the relationship between these conditions in Fig. 3 [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . However, this relationship is not appreciated in Latin America and we will not move forward in this area until data on hypertension in pregnancy is accurately registered and reported in our region.",
